  <title>
  Publish (optional)
  </title>

  <section>
    <title>
    Definition
    </title>

    <para>
    The <emphasis>publish</emphasis> top-level element provides information
    necessary for publishing the final solution, installing the solution on
    production client machines, and updating existing production client
    machines.
    </para>
    
    <para>
    The publish element is based on the Deployment Elements Common Model. See
    <xref linkend="deployment-elements-common-model"/> for a complete
    description of macros, attributes and elements. 
    </para>

    <para>
    Publish is an optional element.
    </para>

  </section>

